    <measure>Success Definition</measure>
    <time_frame>Six Months</time_frame>
    <description>Alive on the originally implanted device at 6 months, and the subject has not had a stroke with a modified Ranking Scale score ≥ 4 (assessed ≥ three months post-stroke event); or
Transplanted by Month 6 and the subject has not had a stroke with modified Ranking Scale score ≥ 4 (assessed ≥ three months post-stroke event); or
Explanted for recovery by Month 6 and the subject has not had a stroke with modified Ranking Scale score ≥ 4 (assessed ≥ three months post-stroke event).</description>
